data.description: Nestled on a peaceful dead-end street, this delightful 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom split-entry home offers you the perfect blend of comfort and tranquility. The spacious living area is bathed in natural light, creating a welcoming atmosphere for family gatherings. The heart of this home is the well-appointed kitchen, boasting newer appliances that make culinary adventures a breeze. The covered back porch provides an ideal spot to relax and unwind. Imagine sipping your morning coffee or enjoying a barbecue with friends while taking in the serene, private backyard. And don't forget about the spectacular sunsets you'll witness from the top of the hill, adding a touch of magic to your evenings. The large laundry room ensures that keeping your clothes clean and organized is a breeze. Conveniently located in South Park, you'll have easy access to parks, shopping, and dining options.
